description: I’m not really sure what to call these monkey text faces but they’re all this very distinct style. The differences between them are how they are decorated. Some are decorated with words, or other characters like stars, umbrellas, hearts, music notes, and whatnot. These decorations are the only way to make different versions of this style monkey emoticon because otherwise they all look the same.
